A program that works a 4*4 square matix with three sub-programs 
1. A sub-program that enters data 
2. A sub-program that updates data 
A. The main diameter and it's conversions to zeros 
B. The data above the main diagonal and it's conversions to zeros
C. The data under the head diameter and converted to zeros 
3. A sub-program that prints the matrices before updating and after the update 
